  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Markdown is dying. And the people killing it built Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0d912b3194570561eda622567082119e1835c92908e346df7a3c28b1ca07ea65",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Last week, Thariq from Anthropic dropped a thesis that broke the dev internet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d88306db07871bf7c911e2568492040c8381d6545aa6e1f488863263b35807b0",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Seven hundred fifty thousand views. The replies split.",
      "checksum": "sha256:713752fbf92e44e2b366846371d7399d11be8ac7d08a1d4260d0baf0c644e933",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 24
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "His claim: markdown is the wrong format.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ae1cb73baa6b36f1c0d65f994baf9ef9663eb50d75fce7b54d4eef34e3e1637a",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 32
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "For every spec, every plan, every P R writeup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:024eb85e917e412ec1a7573cc8eb95241d84686dc7d15aae251e2bb726ed18ec",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Almost all of it. Out. Why? Markdown can carry headings, bold, a bullet list.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b43b8c4d06d2b3eb930fe95df866c437635e8a6e6ab23854626265a5963e1a0e",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 48
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "That is it. H T M L can carry tables. C S S design.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b11c4580549c2574100b781f011e6f698a1fb7fe6664ab770cbb596ef93714c6",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 62
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "S V G charts. Code. Live interactions. Workflows.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2469bcbafbff4849b25863bf85f93f6ee60790dbcf3622c5c042035880d76c92",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 76
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Spatial data. Real images. When you give it H T M L, the agent stops faking the chart and just draws it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e85d535391dcba5d42da5a4557b453f017ebc7d99fdbafbc30ad3259549924c5",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 7.337505668934241,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 84
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Markdown is what your colleague will skim.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a183491659c8249b6c62828670383d931aee011d4054b2b46fee93d36c2a757e",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "H T M L is what your colleague will open.",
      "checksum": "sha256:14e2e57c3439c5fa7c955defdce88f7fb49bab86d5aa0db0752eeb9b57dd9bbd",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 113
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "There are five places where switching to H T M L changes everything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c486c2b40ca13760b223ebeef6b68fb9b5b53090ad83fa7b0e7cce5a230eb775",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 123
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Watch the full video to see why your codebase is about to look very different.",
      "checksum": "sha256:407996f2ae929d0ddccf581670b1849c9381c5fa05e4dc2053050bc9035759e3",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 136
    }
  ]
}